ht on the tongue but heavy on the scale: Glory and praise to Allah, and glory to Allah the Almighty.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7563, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2694 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24471,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/03\/05\/dua-takbir-tasbih-before-asking\/","url_meta":{"origin":500,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Exalt, glorify, praise Allah before asking","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: Umm Sulaym came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and she said, \u201cTeach me some words to say in my prayer.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cExalt Allah ten times, glorify Allah ten times, praise Allah ten times, then ask for whatever you wish. Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5402,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/19\/many-ways-give-charity\/","url_meta":{"origin":500,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Allah made many ways to give charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: Some of\u00a0the companions came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and they said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, the rich have taken all the rewards. They pray as we pray, they fast as we fast, and they give charity from their extra wealth.\u201d The Prophet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17531,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/09\/tasbih-subhanallah-wa-bi-hamdihi\/","url_meta":{"origin":500,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Beloved prayer of the Angels","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked, \"Which statement is best?\" The Prophet said, \u201cIt is what Allah has chosen for His angels and His servants: Glory be to Allah and with His praise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2731 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/500","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=500"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/500\/revision